00:44:01.920 --> 00:44:04.580
within the rules of the game.

00:44:04.580 --> 00:44:08.970
Now in life, if you
don't know something,

00:44:08.970 --> 00:44:12.870
and you can't figure it
out, what can you do?

00:44:12.870 --> 00:44:13.670
AUDIENCE: Guess.

00:44:13.670 --> 00:44:15.340
PROFESSOR: Guess it.

00:44:15.340 --> 00:44:18.080
All right, now this turns out
to be a really good thing to do,

00:44:18.080 --> 00:44:21.757
and especially good in a lot
of computer science situations.

00:44:21.757 --> 00:44:23.590
If you don't know it,
and you can't know it,

00:44:23.590 --> 00:44:28.210
well you could try to guess
and you might be right.

00:44:28.210 --> 00:44:31.570
Now, if you guess x
and you are right,

00:44:31.570 --> 00:44:34.060
what's your
