00:44:35.970 --> 00:44:40.220
If you don't guess x, what's
your probability of winning?

00:44:40.220 --> 00:44:44.100
Say you guess wrong, but
you follow the rule that

00:44:44.100 --> 00:44:46.100
if it's less than what
