00:44:46.100 --> 00:44:47.560
otherwise you don't.

00:44:47.560 --> 00:44:51.370
What's your probability
of winning that?

00:44:51.370 --> 00:44:51.960
P?

00:44:51.960 --> 00:44:55.490
Well, yeah, what's P?

00:44:55.490 --> 00:44:58.840
It's a nice value of P.

00:44:58.840 --> 00:45:00.900
You know, say you
guessed-- well,

00:45:00.900 --> 00:45:04.719
say you weren't paying
attention and you guessed 200.

00:45:04.719 --> 00:45:07.010
And your rule is, if you're
